@robrbecker this is working as intended.

You can easily achieve this by forking the zone and adding this feature. There is no reason for this to be in core. In fact, I have an [example here](https://github.com/angular/zone.js/blob/master/example/counting.html#L29) that does exaclt what you want, but without the API as described here.

I'd be open to publishing a separate `counting-zone.js` that adds such a feature, since it seems like a common use case.

